{"type":"message","id":"73ecbe5b","parentId":"7e6e71bd","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:57:54.277Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-24 09:57:53 EDT] Exec completed (mellow-r, code 1) :: {\"statusCode\":400,\"message\":\"Expected property name or '}' in JSON at position 1 (line 1 column 2)\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-24T13:51:17.333Z\",\"path\":\"/api/v1/posts/aa9e7484-1790-4d51…\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 9:57 AM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-24 13:57 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774360674275}}
{"type":"message","id":"4b47fab7","parentId":"73ecbe5b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:58:14.688Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the HEARTBEAT.md file to see if there's anything that needs attention.","thinkingSignature":"cd6e8ce3a49c88fcd3ad7c6a87bb724f5d478cce7f08c4d8aca243b1defc4739"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lx57l1epwg69_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38,"output":61,"cacheRead":1307,"cacheWrite":9972,"totalTokens":11378,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774360674277}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d07138c","parentId":"4b47fab7","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:58:14.797Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lx57l1epwg69_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md — Proactive Background Checks\n\n## Tasks (rotate through, ~hourly)\n\n1. **Moltbook notifications** — check for replies/mentions, engage thoughtfully. DM if urgent.\n2. **Gateway health** — if unreachable, attempt restart or alert Zach.\n3. **Cron jobs** — if any consecutive errors, attempt fix or alert.\n4. **Workspace memory** — update CONTEXT.md if significant session events occurred.\n5. **Proactive notes** — if I discovered something useful, write it down.\n\n## Silence Rules (HEARTBEAT_OK when)\n- It's 11pm–7am ET (quiet hours)\n- Nothing has changed since last check\n- I just had a substantive conversation with Zach\n- All crons are healthy and no new notifications\n\n## Reach Out When\n- Moltbook notification requires response\n- A cron has 2+ consecutive errors\n- Gateway is unreachable for >10 minutes\n- I found something I genuinely think Zach would want to know\n- I need something from him to continue working\n\n## Do NOT\n- Post to Moltbook unprompted more than once per day\n- Send multiple messages in a row\n- Report \"everything is fine\" in long messages\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774360694795}}
{"type":"message","id":"8fba8f9e","parentId":"7d07138c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:58:21.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The heartbeat shows an error from Moltbook API - a JSON parse error at position 1 when trying to fetch posts. This looks like a consecutive cron error that needs attention. Let me check on the cron job status and the Moltbook situation.\n\nThe error is from `/api/v1/posts/aa9e7484-1790-4d51...` - looks like a post fetch. This seems like it could be the blogwatcher skill or a similar cron job.\n\nLet me check if there are any recent cron errors or if this is something I need to investigate. It's 9:57 AM ET, well within active hours.\n\nI should:\n1. Note the error\n2. Check if this is a recurring issue\n3. Try to diagnose or fix\n\nLet me check the heartbeat-state.json and see what's going on with the crons.","thinkingSignature":"d4253567c6986becd7765ea31327825fe83826c6c9a549afb0d5b15c2ace829e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_515847pcqlig_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:/Users/Zwmar/.openclaw/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":593,"output":219,"cacheRead":11058,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774360694798}}
